Quick steps to see your changes

sudo usermod -aG docker aejakhegbe
sudo systemctl restart docker




Option 1: 
Rebuild and restart (recommended)
sudo docker compose up -d --build frontend

This rebuilds the container (installs new dependencies) and restarts it.

Option 2: Step by step
sudo docker compose up -d frontend


Visit http://localhost:3000

Monitor logs
sudo docker compose logs -f frontend


sudo docker exec -it bridgelearn-frontend sh -c "rm -rf node_modules/.vite"
sudo docker compose restart frontend

